article.description: — George Papas had 31 points as Monmouth defeated Lehigh 85-75 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Papas scores 31 to carry Monmouth over Lehigh 85-75
article.linkText: Papas scores 31 to carry Monmouth over Lehigh 85-75
article.story: WEST LONG BRANCH, N.J. -- — George Papas had 31 points as Monmouth defeated Lehigh 85-75 on Tuesday night. Walker Miller had 19 points and seven rebounds for Monmouth (2-1). Shavar Reynolds Jr. added 16 points. Nikkei Rutty had nine rebounds. Jeameril Wilson tied a career high with 20 points for the Mountain Hawks (0-3). Evan Taylor added 14 points.
